            <title>[MAHOUT-347] org.apache.mahout.math.IndexException: index(-521252222) is out of bounds of (0, 2147483647)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-347</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when run job org.apache.mahout.cf.taste.hadoop.item.RecommenderJob&lt;br/&gt;
get following error:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;10/03/26 09:11:05 INFO mapred.JobClient: Task Id : attempt_201003221228_0170_r_000000_0, Status : FAILED&lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.mahout.math.IndexException: index(-521252222) is out of bounds of (0, 2147483647)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.mahout.math.AbstractVector.set(AbstractVector.java:353)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.mahout.cf.taste.hadoop.item.ToUserVectorReducer.reduce(ToUserVectorReducer.java:75)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.mahout.cf.taste.hadoop.item.ToUserVectorReducer.reduce(ToUserVectorReducer.java:58)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.hadoop.mapred.ReduceTask.runOldReducer(ReduceTask.java:463)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.hadoop.mapred.ReduceTask.run(ReduceTask.java:411)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.hadoop.mapred.Child.main(Child.java:170)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;mahout on linux 64bit&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
